column1: The 3M Company formerly known as the Minnesota Mining and Manufacturing Company is an American multinational conglomerate corporation based in Maplewood Minnesota a suburb of St Paul.
Abbott Laboratories is an American health care company with headquarters in Lake Bluff Illinois United States.

Acuity Brands is a lighting and building management solutions provider headquartered in Atlanta Ga with operations throughout North America and in Europe and Asia.
